  "Description": {
    "English": "Soft workable alloy favored by artisans throughout the known galaxy. Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ionized Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Dioxite</span>.<br><br>A popular trading good, with many galactic shipping paths devoted to its sale and transport.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "易于加工的柔软合金，深受星系中工匠的喜爱。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>制作。<br><br>它是很有销路的商品，星系里很多航路专门用来运输出售这种合金。",
    "TencentChinese": "易于加工的柔软合金，深受星系中工匠的喜爱。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>制作。<br><br>它是很有销路的商品，星系里很多航路专门用来运输出售这种合金。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "柔軟、可塑的合金，深受全銀河系的工匠喜愛。可使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">離子化鈷</span>與<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>製造。<br><br>受歡迎的貿易商品，銀河系中許多貿易路線都是專門運送與銷售這種材料。"
  },
