  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft or refine Grantine from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Dioxite</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Ionized Cobalt</span>. Refining advanced products requires a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Large Refiner</span>.<br>Dioxite is found in large deposits on <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen planets</span> with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br>Refine Ionized Cobalt from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cobalt</span>, which is harvested from <span class=\"name name-technology\">subterranean mineral deposits</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>制作或精炼格兰丁。精炼高级产品需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精炼机</span>。<br>二氧化物能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">冻土星球</span>上使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>在大型矿床中找到。<br>从<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>中精炼出离子钴，钴能从<span class=\"name name-technology\">地下矿床</span>中采集到。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>制作或精炼格兰丁。精炼高级产品需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精炼机</span>。<br>二氧化物能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">冻土星球</span>上使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>在大型矿床中找到。<br>从<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>中精炼出离子钴，钴能从<span class=\"name name-technology\">地下矿床</span>中采集到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">二氧化物</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">離子化鈷</span>製作或精製大鋰。精製高級產品需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">大型精製機</span>。<br>二氧化物能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰寒星球</span>上使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>在大型礦床中找到。<br>從<span class=\"name name-technology\">鈷</span>中精製出離子化鈷，鈷能從<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下礦物沉積</span>中採收到。"
  },
